      *
      * Varible for
     D WSUSER          S             10
     D WSONAVN         S             35
     D JSONstring      s          32000
     D Error           S            150
     D Wtyp            S              3
     D Wkode1          S             20
     D Wkode3          S              5
     D DKIH_25         S              1
     D DKIH_26         S              1
     D AntLest         S              9  0
     d pos             S              5U 0
     D ZB              S              1    DIM(20)

      *get input-string
      /copy syspeds/qrpgsrcpy,prolog3

